SASS Installation Steps:

1. Created the project directory: 0x03-sass_scss
2. Navigated to the project directory
3. Installed SASS using npm:
   npm install sass

Note: The specified version 3.7.4 was not available, so the latest stable version was installed instead.

To compile SASS files, use:
npx sass input.scss output.css

To check SASS version:
npx sass --version
